# QuickMetrics — Blinkit vs Zepto Analytics Dashboard

An interactive analytics dashboard comparing Blinkit and Zepto using real-world quick-commerce datasets. The project analyzes delivery performance, customer behavior, reviews, and operational KPIs through interactive visualizations.

## Live Demo

Dashboard: https://blinkit-zepto-dashboard.vercel.app/

## Data Sources

| File                                     | Rows    | Source                              |
| ---------------------------------------- | ------- | ----------------------------------- |
| blinkit_orders.csv                       | 5,000   | Kaggle — Blinkit Operations Dataset |
| blinkit_customers.csv                    | 2,500   | Same dataset                        |
| blinkit_delivery_performance.csv         | 5,000   | Same dataset                        |
| blinkit_customer_feedback.csv            | 5,000   | Same dataset                        |
| blinkit_marketing_performance.csv        | 5,400   | Same dataset                        |
| quick_commerce_data_modified_cleaned.csv | 947,752 | Kaggle — Quick Commerce India       |
| reviews.csv                              | 4,620   | Real app-store reviews              |

## Key Insights

* Zepto on-time rate: 64.9% vs Blinkit: 14.8%
* Blinkit average delivery time: 15.1 min vs Zepto: 9.6 min
* Blinkit review rating: 2.55⭐ vs Zepto: 1.53⭐
* 23.8% Blinkit customers are inactive (churn risk)
* Traffic is the leading cause of delayed deliveries

## Features

* KPI Dashboard
* Delivery Performance Analysis
* Customer Segmentation
* Revenue Trends
* Customer Feedback Analysis
* Blinkit vs Zepto Comparison
* Interactive Charts and Visualizations

